Grady Sutton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grady_Sutton 0 Grady Harwell Sutton (April 5, 1906 – September 17, 1995) was an American film and television actor from the 1920s to the 1970s. He appeared in more than 180 films. Grady_Harwell_Sutton ( April_5_,_1906 – September_17_,_1995 ) was an_American_film_and_television_actor from the_1920s to the_1970s .
